(273, 1, '2020-04-15 09:59:42', '2020-04-15 09:59:42', '[ux_banner height=\"301px\" bg=\"233\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.17)\" class=\"banner-area-emc\"]\n\n[text_box width=\"59\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\"]\n\n<h5 class=\"banner-t\">We are on a mission to provide children with superior, evidence-based therapy, giving them the skills needed to thrive.</h5>\n<p><img src=\"http://localhost/emc/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/border-b.png\" alt=\"\"class=\"img-fluid\">\n</p>\n<h2>PEDIATRIC SERVICES</p>\n<h2>\n<h5><strong>Enabling each child’s present and future.</strong></h5>\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n[section bg_color=\"rgb(255, 255, 255)\"]\n\n[row style=\"large\" col_style=\"divided\" h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"3\" divider=\"0\" align=\"center\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"243\" img_width=\"130\" pos=\"center\" title=\"Speech Therapy\" icon_border=\"2\" margin=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\"]\n\n<p>The therapist will work with your child on articulation, comprehension, expressive and receptive language, social skills, and other skills to improve communication.</p></p>\n[button text=\"Learn More\" letter_case=\"lowercase\" color=\"white\" style=\"outline\" size=\"large\" radius=\"99\" expand=\"true\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"245\" img_width=\"130\" pos=\"center\" title=\"Occupational Therapy\" icon_border=\"2\" margin=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\"]\n\n<p>Your child will practice activities of daily living (like dressing, eating, hygiene, and organization), fine motor skills, handwriting, and sensory integration skills.</p></p>\n[button text=\"Learn More\" letter_case=\"lowercase\" color=\"white\" style=\"outline\" size=\"large\" radius=\"99\" expand=\"true\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"246\" img_width=\"130\" pos=\"center\" title=\"Physical Therapy\" icon_border=\"2\" margin=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\"]\n\n</p>\n<p>The therapist will keep your child motivated to work on balance, coordination, gross motor skills, stretching, physical manipulation, and strengthening activities.</p></p>\n[button text=\"Learn More\" letter_case=\"lowercase\" color=\"white\" style=\"outline\" size=\"large\" radius=\"99\" expand=\"true\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"247\" img_width=\"130\" pos=\"center\" title=\"Psychology\" icon_border=\"2\" margin=\"0px 0px 0px 0px\"]\n\n<p>The psychologist will provide therapy for behavior management, self-regulation, coping mechanisms, anxiety management, psychotherapy, and other needs.</p></p>\n[button text=\"Learn More\" letter_case=\"lowercase\" color=\"white\" style=\"outline\" size=\"large\" radius=\"99\" expand=\"true\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[ux_banner height=\"400px\" bg_color=\"#d26e4b\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.17)\"]\n\n[text_box text_color=\"dark\" width=\"45\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\" bg=\"rgba(246, 235, 235, 0.86)\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"\">Ask a Therapist</h3>\n<p><strong>Unsure if your child needs therapy? Discuss your concerns and<br />\noptions with a therapist.</strong></p>\n[button text=\"SCHEDULE MY FREE CONSULTATION\" color=\"white\" style=\"outline\" size=\"large\" radius=\"99\" expand=\"0\" link=\"#\"]\n\n<p>\n*This is not a clinical consultation or formal evaluation. There is no obligation to sign on for paid services..</p>\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n[section class=\"why-choose\" bg_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\" padding=\"40px\" height=\"400px\"]\n\n<h2 class=\"why-choose-heading text-center\">Why Choose Enable My Child</h2>\n<h3 class=\"thin-font text-center why-choose-sub-t\">From diagnostics to treatment, Enable My Child is here to support you and your child. Let our experts help.</h3>\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[page_header align=\"center\" title=\"Quality Care\"]\n\n[ux_image_box img=\"262\"]\n\n<p>Teletherapy has been approved by all state accreditation boards as a valid form of service delivery...</p>\n\n[/ux_image_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[page_header align=\"center\" title=\"Best Care\"]\n\n[ux_image_box img=\"265\"]\n\n<p>Your child receives care in the familiarity and comfort of your home. Sessions are scheduled at your.. </p>\n\n[/ux_image_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[page_header align=\"center\" title=\"Affordable Care\" bg_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\"]\n\n[ux_image_box img=\"264\"]\n\n<p>Enable My Child therapy can be more affordable than treatment at a traditional clinic. We are now su.. </p>\n\n[/ux_image_box]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section class=\"parents-corner\" bg_color=\"rgb(184, 180, 180)\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(255,255,255,.5)\" height=\"500px\"]\n\n<div class=\"container\"> \n<h2 class=\"thin-font text-center\">Parent Corner - Coming Soon!</h2><h3 class=\"text-center\">Therapy works better if strategies are implemented throughout your child\'s day. These resources are free so that more children can benefit. Because it\'s the right thing to do.</h3>\n</div>\n[row class=\"parents-corner-sub\"]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n[row_inner v_align=\"middle\"]\n\n[col_inner span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"234\" height=\"auto\"]\n\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<h6>\nScreening</h6>\n<br/>\n<p>\nMonitor your child\'s development with the free EMC screening tool.\n </p>\n\n[/col_inner]\n[col_inner span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"6\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n[section bg_color=\"rgb(241, 241, 241)\" padding=\"43px\" height=\"276px\" border=\"1px 0px 1px 0px\"]\n\n[row v_align=\"equal\"]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<h2 class=\"uppercase\">Latest News</h2>\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod .</p>\n[button text=\"Our blog\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"9\" 